732
00:41:33.630 --> 00:41:37.480
proteasome activity to block mitochondria protein degradation process,

733
00:41:37.930 --> 00:41:41.690
you'll be able to reverse the T cell exhaustion pattern, push

734
00:41:41.730 --> 00:41:45.690
those terminal exhausted T cell regain the expression profile like

