00:41:45.710 --> 00:41:48.209
progenitor exhausted T cell. They have the stemness property.

736
00:41:49.180 --> 00:41:52.370
And we also monitor PI3K/mTOR. We didn't see any difference.

737
00:41:52.710 --> 00:41:52.870
So it

